trans-unit.source: Represents an <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable`1"></xref> collection as an <xref href="System.Linq.IQueryable`1"></xref> data source.
The type of the data in the collection.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Linq.EnumerableQuery`1"></xref> class and associates it with an <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable`1"></xref> collection.
A collection to associate with the new instance.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Linq.EnumerableQuery`1"></xref> class and associates the instance with an expression tree.
An expression tree to associate with the new instance.
Returns a textual representation of the enumerable collection or, if it is null, of the expression tree that is associated with this instance.
A textual representation of the enumerable collection or, if it is null, of the expression tree that is associated with this instance.

Returns an enumerator that can iterate through the associated <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable`1"></xref> collection, or, if it is null, through the collection that results from rewriting the associated expression tree as a query on an <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable`1"></xref> data source and executing it.
An enumerator that can be used to iterate through the associated data source.

Returns an enumerator that can iterate through the associated <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable`1"></xref> collection, or, if it is null, through the collection that results from rewriting the associated expression tree as a query on an <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable`1"></xref> data source and executing it.
An enumerator that can be used to iterate through the associated data source.
Gets the type of the data in the collection that this instance represents.
The type of the data in the collection that this instance represents.
Gets the expression tree that is associated with or that represents this instance.
The expression tree that is associated with or that represents this instance.
Gets the query provider that is associated with this instance.
The query provider that is associated with this instance.

Constructs a new <xref href="System.Linq.EnumerableQuery`1"></xref> object and associates it with a specified expression tree that represents an <xref href="System.Linq.IQueryable"></xref> collection of data.
An expression tree that represents an <xref href="System.Linq.IQueryable"></xref> collection of data.
An object that is associated with expression.

Constructs a new <xref href="System.Linq.EnumerableQuery`1"></xref> object and associates it with a specified expression tree that represents an <xref href="System.Linq.IQueryable`1"></xref> collection of data.
An expression tree to execute.
The type of the data in the collection that expression represents.
An EnumerableQuery object that is associated with expression.

Executes an expression after rewriting it to call <xref href="System.Linq.Enumerable"></xref> methods instead of <xref href="System.Linq.Queryable"></xref> methods on any enumerable data sources that cannot be queried by <xref href="System.Linq.Queryable"></xref> methods.
An expression tree to execute.
The value that results from executing expression.

Executes an expression after rewriting it to call <xref href="System.Linq.Enumerable"></xref> methods instead of <xref href="System.Linq.Queryable"></xref> methods on any enumerable data sources that cannot be queried by <xref href="System.Linq.Queryable"></xref> methods.
An expression tree to execute.
The type of the data in the collection that expression represents.
The value that results from executing expression.
